node.text:
TOMORROW — You don't have to smoke and drink alone! 
Join Juan Lopez and special guest, @bacardi Brand Specialist @chatchowtv, for our weekly #VirtualHerf at 8 PM (EDT)! We’ll be smoking Gurkhas, making three cocktail pairings, giving out prizes, and answering your questions. To follow along with the @therealhavanaclub cocktail recipes, you’ll need:

Cuban Bishop
1½ oz. Havana Club Blanco
½ oz. lime juice
½ oz. simple syrup
½ oz. Sonoma Cabernet Sauvignon

Hemingway Daiquiri
1½ oz. Havana Club Blanco
½ oz. maraschino
3/4 oz. lime juice
½ oz. grapefruit juice
½ oz. cane syrup

Daiquiri
2 oz. Havana Club Blanco
1 oz. lime juice
3/4 oz. cane syrup

Join via Zoom by clicking the link in our bio. #GurkhaNation

ENDS TOMORROW — Are you an avid grilling enthusiast AND Gurkha or @sindicatocigars smoker? Then enter our “Grill with Gurkha” photo contest by sharing your best photo grilling with a Gurkha or Sindicato cigar, and you could win a set of Gurkha cutlery knives, Gurkha steak knives, and Gurkha growler!

Eligibility: Entries accepted on Instagram/Twitter @GurkhaCigars with #GrillWithGurkha or Facebook.com/GurkhaCigars until August 9 at 11:59 AM (EDT).
